invalid type: string "BraTS 2024 challenge dataset contains multi-parametric MRI scans from post-operative GBM patients. The dataset includes T1, T1CE, T2, and FLAIR sequences with expert segmentation labels for enhancing tumor (ET), tumor core (TC), and whole tumor (WT) regions. Feature vectors extracted using CNN-ViT architectures achieve AUC 0.87 for progression prediction at 6-month follow-up.